22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETurning%20on%20dark%20mode%20will%20give%20the%20app%20a%20dark%20background%20with%20light%20text.%20Dark%20mode%20provides%20a%20visually%20appealing%20and%20potentially%20eye-friendly%20alternative%20to%20the%20standard%20light%20theme.%20By%20reducing%20screen%20brightness%20and%20contrast%2C%20dark%20mode%20can%20help%20reduce%20eye%20strain%2C%20especially%20in%20low-light%20environments.%20Dark%20mode%20doesn't%20change%20the%20way%20videos%20look%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20feature%20can%20be%20managed%20from%20%3Cstrong%3ESettings%20and%20privacy%20%26gt%3B%20Display.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22link%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.tiktok.com%2Fen%2Faccount-and-privacy%2Faccount-privacy-settings%2Fdark-mode%22%2C%22learnMore%22%3A%22Learn%20more%20about%20dark%20mode%22%2C%22image%22%3A%7B%22name%22%3A%22Dark%20Mode%22%2C%22description%22%3Anull%2C%22urls%22%3A%7B%22sg%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fp16-ttark-sg.tiktokcdn.com%2Ftos-alisg-i-0twjg7x6w4-sg%2F6c1d2fc97bcfa84cd117916c745f95c1.png~tplv-0twjg7x6w4-default%3A0%3A0%3Aq75.image%22%2C%22va%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fp16-ttak-va.tiktokcdn.com%2Ftos-maliva-i-m3rm1y8daf-us%2F6c1d2fc97bcfa84cd117916c745f95c1.png~tplv-m3rm1y8daf-default%3A0%3A0%3Aq75.image%22%2C%22gcp%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fp16-ttark-useastred.tiktokcdn-eu.com%2Ftos-useast2a-i-mysv9ld3jo-euttp%2F6c1d2fc97bcfa84cd117916c745f95c1.png~tplv-mysv9ld3jo-default%3A0%3A0%3Aq75.image%22%2C%22ie%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fp16-headlessx-image-no.tiktokcdn-eu.com%2Ftos-no1a-i-tmgzy48pwj-no%2F6c1d2fc97bcfa84cd117916c745f95c1.png~tplv-tmgzy48pwj-default%3A0%3A0%3Aq75.image%22%2C%22ttp%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fp16-ttark.tiktokcdn-us.com%2Ftos-useast5-i-1rzkm2vceq-tx%2F6c1d2fc97bcfa84cd117916c745f95c1.png~tplv-1rzkm2vceq-default%3A0%3A0%3Aq75.image%22%2C%22ttp2%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fp16-ttark-useast8.tiktokcdn-us.com%2Ftos-useast8-i-zr23xo8qx2-tx2%2F6c1d2fc97bcfa84cd117916c745f95c1.png~tplv-zr23xo8qx2-default%3A0%3A0%3Aq75.image%22%7D%7D%7D